name: Alby: Genesis 0,0
description: Alby Wistar, Genesis. This piece marks the 1st NFT in the Alby collections and AlbyWistar series of works. Alby is inspired by and created as a commentary on the human condition and society. A comparison of social environment, behaviours and structure to the life of the lab rat. Despite the potential negative connotations of this interpretation and imagery; uniqueness, purpose and enjoyment of life should be neither considered vane or futile. Yet, must be checked against morality and mortality.
